  "full_text": "An update for boost is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe boost packages contain a large number of free peer-reviewed portable C++ source libraries. These libraries are suitable for tasks such as portable file-systems, time/date abstraction, serialization, unit testing, thread creation and multi-process synchronization, parsing, graphing, regular expression manipulation, and many others.Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s): RHEL9.6 - boost-json: json parsing bug with boost of integer values [rhel-9.7.z] (JIRA:RHEL-120655)"
